RG 1.16 A limited financial services licence may authorise you to provide one or more
of the following limited financial services:
(a) provide financial product advice about interests in a self-managed
superannuation fund (SMSF) or a holder's existing interest in a
superannuation product;
(b) provide class of product advice on any of the following:
(i) superannuation products;
(ii) securities;
(iii) simple managed investment schemes;
(iv) general insurance products;
(v) life risk insurance products; and
(vi) basic deposit products;
