(c) arrange for another person to deal in an interest in an SMSF.
Note: 'Limited financial services' is defined in regs 7.8.12A(4) and 7.8.14B(3) of the
Corporations Regulations. You can find a copy of the Corporations Regulations on the
Federal Register of Legislation.
